eky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/K%C3%BD-L%C3%BD-t%C6%B0-kh%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B9/poem-QXPAlwbtLj2tg3Hb0QeI7g">Ký Lý tư không kỹ - 贈李司空妓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/author-EjtGFCLaQR-cL2GZdcpbaQ">Lưu Vũ Tích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/Nh%E1%BA%ADm-Kh%C3%A2u-ng%E1%BB%99-V%C5%A9-t%C6%B0-t%C3%A2n-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C6%A1-quy-t%E1%BB%B1-M%C3%A2n-Nam-d%C4%A9-m%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%AD-l%E1%BB%87-chi-ph%C3%A2n-h%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng/poem-YZ8n6uJCkCTgU3JQTZ7fFg">Nhậm Khâu ngộ Vũ tư tân Thượng Cơ quy tự Mân Nam dĩ mật tí lệ chi phân hướng - 任丘遇禹司賔尚基歸自閩南以蜜漬茘枝分餉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/author-9xzWBLqDsfopprRgu6Tsgg">Tra Thận Hành</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B7-ho%C3%A0i/poem-aTahOnZk3Eon3zYPAhc_Gg">Thập nhất nhật kỷ hoài - 十一日紀懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-phi/poem-XB7qfURCXRa4fhA6_KeeiQ">Tương phi - 湘妃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
